This is the repository for transforming antiX Linux into Swift Linux.

To download this repository and other repositories, open a regular user shell and enter:
mkdir ~/develop
cd ~/develop
git clone git@github.com:swiftlinux/1-build.git
sh get_reps_diet.sh

desktop-diet.sh: Transforms the desktop installation of antiX Linux into Diet Swift Linux

build-diet.sh: Transforms the antiX Linux ISO file into the Diet Swift Linux ISO file

shared-diet.sh: The core elements of transforming antiX Linux into Diet Swift Linux; shared by desktop-diet.sh and build-diet.sh
